Creating New Form

Learn how to create new form and add validation.

Step 1: Click on "Builder" link

Step 2: Click on "Create New Form" button

Step 3: Click on "e.g., Customer Feedback"

Step 4: Type "My Form" in "Form Name" field

Step 5: Click element

Step 6: Click on "Create Form" button

Step 7: Type "chat" in "Chat" field

Step 8: Click on "Add Field" button

Step 9: Click on "Text" button

Step 10: Click on "Text"

Step 11: Type "What is your name?" in "Write here..." field

Step 12: Click on "Validation" button

Step 13: Click on "Attributes" button

Step 14: Click on "+ Add Attribute" button

Step 15: Click on "Attribute (e.g. placeholder)"

Step 16: Click on "Field Settings Editor General Advanced"

Step 17: Type "maxlength" in "Attribute (e.g. placeholder)" field

Step 18: Click on "+ Add Attribute"

Step 19: Click on "Value"

Step 20: Type "3" in "Value" field

Step 21: Click on "Field Settings Editor General Advanced"

Step 22: Click on "Save" button

Step 23: Click on "Open"

Step 24: Click element

Step 25: Type "Nab" in "field_0" field

Step 26: Click on "field_0" field
